title: #118 - Kurt Braunohler & ME
description: Comedian Kurt Braunohler & I hang out in the Mancave - I make him retell a great story I heard him tell on This American Life, we talk about his Jet ski ride from Chicago to New Orleans, and we conspire to drive to Bisbee to hang out with Stanhope.
